\c 20
\s Umfanekiso wezisebenzi zesivini
\p
\v 1 Ngoba umbuso wamazulu ufanana lomuntu ongumninindlu\x + 19.27.\x*, owaphuma ekuseni kakhulu ukuqhatsha izisebenzi ziye esivinini sakhe\x + 21.28,33.\x*;
\v 2 esevumelene lezisebenzi \w ngodenariyo\w** ngosuku, wazithuma esivinini sakhe.
\v 3 Wasephuma sekungaba lihola \w lesithathu\w**, wabona abanye bemi emdangeni bengenzi lutho;
\v 4 lakulabo wathi: Yanini lani esivinini; njalo loba yini efaneleyo ngizalinika yona. Bahamba-ke.
\v 5 Wabuya waphuma sekungaba lihola \w lesithupha\w** langelesificamunwemunye, wenza njalo.
\v 6 Kwathi sekungaba lihola \w letshumi\w** lanye waphuma, wathola abanye bemi bengenzi lutho, wathi kubo: Limeleni lapha usuku lonke lingenzi lutho\x + 1 Kor. 15.8.\x*?
\v 7 Bathi kuye: Ngoba akulamuntu osiqhatshileyo\x + Seb. 14.16; 17.30.\x*. Wathi kubo: Yanini lani esivinini, njalo lizakwemukela loba kuyini okufaneleyo.
\v 8 Kwathi sekuntambama umninisivini wathi enduneni yakhe\x + Levi 19.13.\x*: Biza izisebenzi, uzibhadale iholo, uqale ngezokucina kuze kube ngezokuqala\x + Luka 8.3. Gal.4.2.\x*.
\v 9 Kuthe befika aba\add qhatshwa\add* ngehola letshumi lanye ngulowo lalowo wemukela udenariyo.
\v 10 Njalo sebezile abokuqala bacabanga ukuthi bazakwemukela okungaphezulu; kodwa labo bemukela udenariyo ngamunye.
\v 11 Kwathi be\add ye\add*mukela bamsola umninindlu\x + 24.43. Mark. 14.14. Luka 12.39; 22.11.\x*,
\v 12 besithi: Labo abokucina basebenze ihola elilodwa, kodwa ubalinganise lathi\x + Ruthe 2.19. 2 Kho. 12.11.\x* esithwele ubunzima bosuku lokutshisa\x + Jak. 1.11.Gen. 31.40.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa ephendula wathi komunye wabo: Mngane, angikoni; kanti kawuvumelananga lami ngodenariyo\x + 11.16. 22.12; 26.50.\x*?
\v 14 Thatha okwakho uhambe; ngiyathanda ukumnika lowokucina njengawe\x + 25.25.\x*.
\v 15 Kumbe angivunyelwa yini ukwenza engikuthandayo ngezinto zami\x + Roma 9.20-24.\x*? Loba ilihlo lakho libi yini\x + 6.23.\x*, ngoba mina ngilungile\x + Luka 6.35. 1 Pet. 2.3.\x*?
\v 16 Kunjalo-ke abokucina bazakuba ngabokuqala, labokuqala ngabokucina\x + 19.30.\x*; ngoba banengi ababiziweyo, kodwa balutshwana abakhethiweyo\x + 22.14. Isam. 17.14.\x*.
\s UJesu ukhuluma ngokuhlupheka kwakhe
\p
\v 17 Kwathi uJesu\x + Mark. 10.32-34. Luka 18.31-34.\x* esesenyukela eJerusalema wathatha abalitshumi lambili bebodwa endleleni, wathi kubo\x + Luka 2.4.\x*:
\v 18 Khangelani, senyukela eJerusalema\x + 16.21.\x*, njalo iNdodana yomuntu izanikelwa kubapristi abakhulu lakubabhali; besebeyilahlela ukufa\x + 20.18,19.\x*,
\v 19 bayinikele\x + 20.18,19.\x* kwabezizwe\x + 27.2. Mark. 15.1. Luka 23.1. Joha. 18.28-32. Seb. 3.13.\x* ukuze ba\add yi\add*yangise ba\add yi\add*tshaye ngesiswepu ba\add yi\add*bethele\x + 27.26-31.\x*; njalo ngosuku lwesithathu izabuya ivuke\x + 27.63.\x*.
\s UJesu ukhuza amadodana kaZebediya
\p
\v 20 Kwasekusiza kuye unina\x + Mark. 10.35-45.\x* wamadodana kaZebediya kanye lamadodana akhe\x + 4.21. Mark. 10.35.\x*, waguqa wacela ulutho kuye\x + 8.2.\x*.
\v 21 Wasesithi kuye: Ufunani? Wathi kuye: Tshono ukuthi la amadodana ami amabili ahlale\x + 19.28.\x*, enye ngakwesokunene sakho\x + 25.34.\x*, lenye ngakwesokhohlo, embusweni wakho.
\v 22 Kodwa uJesu waphendula wathi: Kalikwazi elikucelayo. Linganatha yini inkezo engizayinatha mina\x + 26.39,42. Isa. 51.22. Mark. 14.36. Luka 22.42. Joha. 18.11.\x*, njalo libhabhathizwe ngobhabhathizo engibhabhathizwa ngalo mina\x + Luka 12.50.\x*? Bathi kuye: Singa\add kwenza\add*.
\v 23 Wasesithi kubo: Ngeqiniso lizayinatha inkezo yami, libhabhathizwe ngobhabhathizo mina engizabhabhathizwa ngalo\x + Seb. 12.2. Isam. 1.9.\x*; kodwa ukuhlala ngakwesokunene sami langakwesokhohlo sami, kayisikho okwami ukuphana ngakho, kodwa \add kungo\add*kwalabo\x + 19.11.\x* abakulungiselweyo nguBaba\x + 25.34.\x*.
\s Ubukhulu obuqotho
\p
\v 24 Kwathi sebezwile abalitshumi, bathukuthela ngezelamani ezimbili.
\v 25 Kodwa uJesu wababizela kuye wathi: Liyazi ukuthi ababusi bezizwe\x + Luka 22.25-27.\x* bayazibusa ngobulukhuni, lezikhulu zisebenzisa amandla phezu kwazo\x + 1 Pet.5.3.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa akuyikuba njalo phakathi kwenu; kodwa loba ngubani othanda ukuba ngomkhulu phakathi kwenu\x + Mark. 9.35.\x* kabe yisisebenzi senu\x + 22.13; 23.11. Mark. 9.35.Luka 22.26.\x*;
\v 27 njalo loba ngubani othanda ukuba ngowokuqala phakathi kwenu kabe yisisebenzi senu;
\v 28 njengalokhu iNdodana yomuntu kayizanga ukukhonzwa, kodwa ukukhonza\x + Luka 22.27. Joha. 13.4,13-15. Fil. 2.7.\x*, lokunika impilo yayo ibe lihlawulo\x + Isa. 53.10. Dan. 9.26. Joha. 11.51,52. 1 Tim. 2.6. Tit. 2.14. 1 Pet. 1.19.\x* labanengi\x + 26.28. Isa. 53.11. Heb. 2.10; 9.28. 1 Tim. 2.6.\x*.
\s UJesu usilisa iziphofu ezimbili
\p
\v 29 Kwathi\x + Mark. 10.46-52. Luka 18.35-43.\x* bephuma\x + Luka 18.35; 19.1.\x* eJeriko, ixuku elikhulu lamlandela\x + Luka 10.30; 19.1. Heb. 11.30. 1 Kho. 16.34.\x*.
\v 30 Njalo khangela, iziphofu ezimbili zihlezi endleleni, sezizwile ukuthi uJesu uyadlula, zamemeza, zathi: Sihawukele, Nkosi, Ndodana kaDavida\x + 9.27-31. Mark. 10.46. Luka 18.35.\x*!
\v 31 Ixuku laselizikhuza ukuthi zithule, kodwa zamemeza kakhulu, zisithi: Sihawukele, Nkosi, Ndodana kaDavida\x + Mark. 10.48. Luka 18.39.\x*!
\v 32 UJesu wasesima wazibiza, wathi: Lifuna ukuthi ngilenzeleni?
\v 33 Zathi kuye: Nkosi, ukuthi amehlo ethu avuleke.
\v 34 UJesu esesiba lesihelo wathinta amehlo azo; njalo amehlo azo ahle abuya abona, zasezimlandela\x + 9.29. 8.3,15. Mark. 1.41; 7.33; 8.23,25. Luka 5.13; 22.51. Joha. 9.6.\x*.